    <Name>Rogue</Name>
    <Description>Rogues get the most skill points in the game. They are capable of
finding and disarming traps and opening locks. The rogue can also
deal devastating sneak attack damage when they are beneath the
notice of their enemies and are the best at stealth and sneaking
around. Their defenses are quite low, even though they have
Evasion and a fairly high Dodge, and so must rely on their wits
and cunning to survive tough battles. Rogues can do well as either
a melee or ranged character, and their primary attributes are
Dexterity and Intelligence.</Description>
