    <Feat>
      <Name>Defensive Roll</Name>
      <Description>Grants the Rogue a chance to cheat death when critically injured.
When below 20% health, a Rogue with Defensive Roll has a chance equal to their
total Reflex Save Modifier of taking half damage from melee or ranged weapon attacks
and negating any special effects associated with the attack as if the Rogue were blocking.
Defensive Roll is subject to the same armor and encumbrance restrictions as the
Evasion class skill.</Description>
